@start
Hey, <face:smile>
How are you? {
    ?: Doing well!
        That is great to hear. <face:pleased>
    ?: Not great.
        @bad
        Sorry to hear that. <face:weary>
        -> elsewhere
    ?: I've been... {
        ?: Worse
            Hey that's a start! <face:smile>
        ?: Better
            -> bad
    }
    ?: I won't say
        Why is that? {
            ?: Don't feel like it!
                Verywell...
            ?: I don't know you!
                You will!
        }
}
-> wrapup

@elsewhere
If you ever want to talk about it,
Do not hesitate to.
@wrapup
Well thats it for this test... <face:weary>
-> start